that the past 100 days have given hope and opportunity for
different relations with Lebanon and Syria, which is the major
foreign power broker in Lebanon and had related its peace talks
with Israel to Israeli withdrawal from Lebanon. (Israel-Lebanon-
Withdrawal) 
</P>
