<P>
ISLAMABAD, September 3 (Xinhua) -- At least seven persons
including a woman were killed, while 29 other sustained injuries
in a road accident at Minhasa near Dheerkot in district Bagh, some
50 kilometers from Muzaffarabad in Pakistan-administered Kashmir
on Sunday.
</P>
