<HEADLINE> Philippine President to Attend U.N. Summit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, September 3 (Xinhua) -- Philippine President Joseph
Estrada will leave Monday for New York to attend the United
Nations Millennium Summit starting Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
As part of his diplomatic and trade mission, Estrada will also
make a working visit to San Francisco, Chicago and Honolulu during
